Products.FullDescription: From The Deli Platter For Two
Products.RichDescription:
Serves 2 people

Our Entertaining platters are made fresh to order in store for Delivery or Pick up. Please allow 36 hours notice when ordering (or 48 hours for Public Holidays, including Christmas and Easter).

This Grazing Platter has the perfect mix of cheese and deli meats to make it a perfect accompaniment to drinks and aperitif, as well as the first course to a relaxed social gathering. The array of mouthwatering nibbles, makes it just as easy to match with either bubbles, crisp dry white or red wines.

Products.RichDescription: Our premium saltwater Barramundi is nurtured on our family farm, halfway between Darwin and Kakadu National Park. Sustainable farming techniques run deep to the core of Humpty Doo Barramundi's operations. From sustainably-sourced feed to recirculating our water through a purpose-built wetland, our high quality premium saltwater grown Barramundi is produced while protecting our unique surrounding environment. Humpty Doo Barramundi is a superb eating quality Barramundi with a delicate flavour and clean, firm fillet which remains moist when cooked. Humpty Doo Barramundi is a good source of omega 3 fatty acids, phosphorus (for energy) and selenium (for a healthy immune system), making it the perfect choice for you and your family.
